8. Move the pack of Alpen Salt to a cabinet.

10. Move the box of Rice Bubbles to a cabinet.
11. Identify the box of shortbread on the countertop.

13. Identify the duplicate jar of jam on the countertop.

15. Identify the stack of paper plates on the countertop.
16. Move the stack of paper plates to a cabinet.
17. Move to the dining room.
18. Inspect the table.
19. Identify the two bottles of water on the table.
20. Move one bottle of water to the refrigerator.
21. Move the second bottle of water to the refrigerator.
22. Identify the bowl of fruit on the table.
23. Move the bowl of fruit to a cabinet or pantry (not specified).
24. Identify the cookbook on the table.
25. Move the cookbook to a designated book storage or a cabinet.
